117
00:09:29,069 --> 00:09:30,369
What a waste.

118
00:09:32,406 --> 00:09:34,825
(tense music)

119
00:09:57,764 --> 00:10:00,225
I heard good things
about this Justin Vanier.

120
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:02,110
