140
00:10:50,317 --> 00:10:52,027
Try it again, you'll get the hang of it.

141
00:10:53,737 --> 00:10:54,496
Yes, sir. Thank you.

142
00:10:54,696 --> 00:10:55,330
Yes, sir.

143
00:10:55,530 --> 00:10:56,748
Justin.

144
00:10:56,948 --> 00:10:58,083
How you doin', sir?

145
00:10:58,283 --> 00:10:59,460
Woods.

146
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:00,711
Let's go talk over there.

147
00:11:00,911 --> 00:11:02,337
