you give him to choose from.

188
00:13:13,668 --> 00:13:14,553
One two, one two.

189
00:13:14,753 --> 00:13:16,922
Complete punches, front kick.

190
00:13:21,593 --> 00:13:22,352
Hey!

191
00:13:22,552 --> 00:13:23,645
Are you trying to kill him?

192
00:13:23,845 --> 00:13:25,439
(computer beeps)
Get me in there!

193
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:26,732
Link me up now!

194
00:13:26,932 --> 00:13:29,142
(Eric yells)

195
00:13:32,437 --> 00:13:33,980
That still was level two!

196
00:13:34,314 --> 00:13:35,073
Sorry.

197
00:13:35,273 --> 00:13:36,366
It's a glitch.

198
00:13:36,566 --> 00:13:37,866
Glitch my...

