take the afternoon class?

205
00:14:00,507 --> 00:14:01,350
Sure.

206
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:02,517
Thanks.

207
00:14:02,717 --> 00:14:04,137
Come on, I'll buy you lunch.

208
00:14:07,389 --> 00:14:08,482
(beeping)

209
