there's a connection?

233
00:15:14,372 --> 00:15:15,672
To the agent?

234
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,800
I doubt it.

235
00:15:20,462 --> 00:15:21,762
Hmm.

236
00:15:22,339 --> 00:15:25,008
(dramatic music)

237
00:15:25,967 --> 00:15:28,720
(people chanting)

238
00:15:40,106 --> 00:15:42,359
