deliver what you say.

250
00:16:18,895 --> 00:16:19,738
Well...

251
00:16:19,938 --> 00:16:21,690
You're not here because
you think we can't,

252
00:16:22,023 --> 00:16:23,492
are you, Mr. Bromfield?

253
00:16:23,692 --> 00:16:25,118
What Mr. Bromfield is saying

254
00:16:25,318 --> 00:16:26,870
