of my staff's abilities.

257
00:16:35,578 --> 00:16:36,878
Would you like that?

258
00:16:37,414 --> 00:16:38,714
If it's possible.

259
00:16:42,585 --> 00:16:44,137
Ah, I got just the thing.

260
00:16:46,339 --> 00:16:50,343
(Damian grunts)
(man gasps)

261
00:16:50,677 --> 00:16:51,977
Jesus.

262
00:16:53,304 --> 00:16:56,307
