606
00:36:52,169 --> 00:36:52,803
Yes!

607
00:36:53,003 --> 00:36:54,471
We'll use the other door.

608
00:36:54,671 --> 00:36:57,466
(suspenseful music)

609
00:37:03,597 --> 00:37:04,356
I've got it.

610
00:37:04,556 --> 00:37:06,391
- Right.
- Let's go.

611
00:37:06,725 --> 00:37:09,019
(tense music)

