685
00:44:11,483 --> 00:44:12,825
Try one of these.

686
00:44:14,235 --> 00:44:15,535
Do you like that?

687
00:44:15,945 --> 00:44:18,907
(electricity surges)

688
00:44:22,827 --> 00:44:24,913
(computer beeps)

689
00:44:25,246 --> 00:44:26,546
Oh, man.

690
00:44:28,833 --> 00:44:30,133
Maybe.

691
00:44:33,254 --> 00:44:35,674
(Vicki types)

692
00:44:37,217 --> 00:44:38,517
