712
00:46:24,449 --> 00:46:25,208
Woo hoo!

713
00:46:25,408 --> 00:46:26,708
Woo!

714
00:46:27,577 --> 00:46:30,079
(men grunting)

715
00:46:34,125 --> 00:46:36,294
Think you are pretty good, eh?

716
00:46:36,628 --> 00:46:38,387
