717
00:46:43,009 --> 00:46:45,512
(men grunting)

718
00:46:59,234 --> 00:46:59,993
(computer beeps)

719
00:47:00,193 --> 00:47:01,493
Oh, my God.

720
00:47:02,946 --> 00:47:04,164
