to Warbeck how I feel.

728
00:47:21,339 --> 00:47:21,973
Count on it.

729
00:47:22,173 --> 00:47:23,308
You do the same for me, okay?

730
00:47:23,508 --> 00:47:24,808
You got it.

731
00:47:25,343 --> 00:47:30,265
(intense music)
(thunder rumbles)

732
